ing and ending periods, for budgeting and budget control on the <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Budget cycle time span<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> page.","pos":[3725,3895],"source":"After basic budgeting is configured, you can define the time, or the starting and ending periods, for budgeting and budget control on the **Budget cycle time span** page."},{"content":"Budget cycles often correspond to fiscal calendars but can span fiscal years.","pos":[3896,3973]},{"content":"<ph id=\"ph1\">![</ph>BudgetCycleTimeSpans<ph id=\"ph2\">](./media/budgetcycletimespans-300x157.png)</ph> The next steps in the configuration are completed on the various tabs on the <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Budget control configuration<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> page.","pos":[3974,4155],"source":"![BudgetCycleTimeSpans](./media/budgetcycletimespans-300x157.png) The next steps in the configuration are completed on the various tabs on the **Budget control configuration** page."},{"pos":[4161,4178],"content":"Define parameters","linkify":"Define parameters","nodes":[{"content":"Define parameters","pos":[0,17]}]},{"content":"Based on the financial dimensions that are enabled for the budget, you can use all the financial dimensions for budget control or a subset of them.","pos":[4180,4327]},{"content":"Additionally, you can specify the default time interval (for example, <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Fiscal year<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept>, <bpt id=\"p2\">**</bpt>Fiscal year to date<ept id=\"p2\">**</ept>, <bpt id=\"p3\">**</bpt>Fiscal period<ept id=\"p3\">**</ept>, or <bpt id=\"p4\">**</bpt>Quarterly<ept id=\"p4\">**</ept>) that budget control will be performed for in the related budget cycle time span.","pos":[4328,4557],"source":" Additionally, you can specify the default time interval (for example, **Fiscal year**, **Fiscal year to date**, **Fiscal period**, or **Quarterly**) that budget control will be performed for in the related budget cycle time span."},{"content":"You can also specify a default budget manager and the threshold that is used to notify users when the threshold has been reached.","pos":[4558,4687]},{"content":"The values in these fields will be used as default values in any new budget control rule or budget group that is created.","pos":[4688,4809]},{"content":"However, the default values can be changed for individual groups or rules.","pos":[4810,4884]},{"content":"The ways that budgets are created and recorded in the budget register help determine the time span that is selected when available budget funds are evaluated.","pos":[4885,5043]},{"content":"If an annualized amount for a dimension value combination is developed and used, a fiscal-year or fiscal-year-to-date approach might make sense.","pos":[5044,5188]},{"content":"However, if an organization that creates budgets by fiscal period or allocates to fiscal periods wants more detailed control, it might want to consider fiscal-period-to-date or quarterly time spans.","pos":[5189,5387]},{"content":"In addition, an organization’s culture, as it's related to budgeting and budgetary control, also helps define the configuration.","pos":[5388,5516]},{"content":"<bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt><ph id=\"ph1\">![</ph>BudgetControlConfigurationParameters<ept id=\"p1\">](./media/budgetcontrolconfigurationparameters-300x220.png)](./media/budgetcontrolconfigurationparameters.png)</ept>","pos":[5517,5666],"source":"[![BudgetControlConfigurationParameters](./media/budgetcontrolconfigurationparameters-300x220.png)](./media/budgetcontrolconfigurationparameters.png)"},{"pos":[5672,5695],"content":"Over budget permissions","linkify":"Over budget permissions","nodes":[{"content":"Over budget permissions","pos":[0,23]}]},{"content":"Next, on the <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Over budget permissions<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> tab, you can specify user groups.","pos":[5697,5771],"source":"Next, on the **Over budget permissions** tab, you can specify user groups."},{"content":"You can also specify whether users who are members of a group have permission to exceed the budget.","pos":[5772,5871]},{"content":"You can prevent users from exceeding the budget past the budget threshold that was set on the <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Budget parameters<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> page, or you can prevent them from exceeding the budget by any amount, regardless of the threshold.","pos":[5872,6087],"source":" You can prevent users from exceeding the budget past the budget threshold that was set on the **Budget parameters** page, or you can prevent them from exceeding the budget by any amount, regardless of the threshold."},{"content":"Depending on how proactively an organization manages its spending, these permissions can help it manage its financial resources.","pos":[6088,6216]},{"content":"<bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt><ph id=\"ph1\">![</ph>OverBudgetPermissions<ept id=\"p1\">](./media/overbudgetpermissions-300x149.png)](./media/overbudgetpermissions.png)</ept>","pos":[6217,6321],"source":"[![OverBudgetPermissions](./media/overbudgetpermissions-300x149.png)](./media/overbudgetpermissions.png)"},{"pos":[6327,6349],"content":"Budget funds available","linkify":"Budget funds available","nodes":[{"content":"Budget funds available","pos":[0,22]}]},{"content":"Next, on the <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Budget funds available<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> tab, you can define the formula that is used to calculate available budget funds.","pos":[6351,6472],"source":"Next, on the **Budget funds available** tab, you can define the formula that is used to calculate available budget funds."},{"content":"Depending on how conservatively an organization manages its financial resources, or depending on regulations or industry requirements, the calculation can include draft or unposted documents.","pos":[6473,6664]},{"content":"<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Note:<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> If the calculation is modified during a budget cycle, the changes won't affect any documents that previously passed the budget control checks, and that were posted or completed.","pos":[6665,6852],"source