budget check is performed for the amounts and accounts on a purchase line, the budget control category that is assigned to the reservation is **Encumbrance**."},{"content":"When a budget check is performed for the amounts and accounts on a purchase requisition, the budget control category that is assigned to the reservation is <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Pre-encumbrance<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept>.","pos":[7650,7826],"source":" When a budget check is performed for the amounts and accounts on a purchase requisition, the budget control category that is assigned to the reservation is **Pre-encumbrance**."},{"content":"If <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Budget reservations for encumbrance<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> and/or <bpt id=\"p2\">**</bpt>Budget reservations for pre-encumbrance<ept id=\"p2\">**</ept> is included in the calculation of available budget funds and must be reflected through postings in the general ledger, you should enable commitment accounting on the <bpt id=\"p3\">**</bpt>General ledger parameters<ept id=\"p3\">**</ept> page.","pos":[7827,8122],"source":" If **Budget reservations for encumbrance** and/or **Budget reservations for pre-encumbrance** is included in the calculation of available budget funds and must be reflected through postings in the general ledger, you should enable commitment accounting on the **General ledger parameters** page."},{"content":"<bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt><ph id=\"ph1\">![</ph>DocumentsAndJournals<ept id=\"p1\">](./media/documentsandjournals-300x99.png)](./media/documentsandjournals.png)</ept>","pos":[8123,8223],"source":"[![DocumentsAndJournals](./media/documentsandjournals-300x99.png)](./media/documentsandjournals.png)"},{"pos":[8229,8249],"content":"Assign budget models","linkify":"Assign budget models","nodes":[{"content":"Assign budget models","pos":[0,20]}]},{"content":"Next, on the <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Assign budget models<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> tab, you assign budget models to the budget cycle time spans that should be included in budget